<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٠٣ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو عَوَانَةَ، عَنْ قَتَادَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَنَسٍ <span class="special">﵁</span>:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> رَأَى رَجُلًا يَسُوقُ بَدَنَةً،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ لَهُ:</span> <span class="c2">(ارْكَبْهَا)</span>.<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> يَا رَسُولَ اللَّهِ إِنَّهَا بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ فِي الثَّالِثَةِ أَوْ الرَّابِعَةِ:</span> <span class="c2">(ارْكَبْهَا وَيْلَكَ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ:</span> وَيْحَكَ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
